// Diagrams Tab
// Client-side Mermaid rendering for the Diagrams tab of the onboarding topic detail view.
// Renders each DiagramBlock as a titled card with inline SVG output.

FUNCTION DiagramsTab(diagrams)                                          EXPORT
  CALLS: MermaidDiagram (DiagramsTab)
  If no diagrams are provided, show a "No diagrams available" placeholder.
  ELSE render a MermaidDiagram for each diagram block.

---

FUNCTION MermaidDiagram(diagram, index)
  On mount or diagram.content change: call mermaid.render with a unique ID and inject the resulting SVG.
  IF rendering fails: show the error message and a collapsible source code view.
  Show the diagram title (if present) in a header bar above the SVG.
